&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="summary">Summary&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>The Response API is a straightforward way to generate text with OpenAI. Check the docs, prepare an API key, and try the Python SDK for a smooth start.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>